 <br />\n好想知佢當我係咩"},{"pid":"217426ef76e6fc2099671b25634b6c353831e4e4","tid":202650,"uid":84936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"你愈緊張佢越覺得你可有可無<br />\n唔好搵佢啦！"},{"pid":"a79107e607f618a8537f5473c54d72bd0fe23c72","tid":202650,"uid":47146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你愈緊張佢越覺得你可有可無<br />\n唔好搵佢啦！</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好 我唔會再搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62317614af48754b35ab09629f4ec436ad2ed155","tid":202650,"uid":31442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:45:01.000Z","msg":"block曬佢啲嘢，如果唔係，你只會比佢當你狗咁撚，無限輪迴，永遠都走唔到。"}]}